Excellent! The web search confirms my understanding. In Tailwind CSS v4, you need to use `@custom-variant` (or `@variant`) to configure the dark mode selector. The syntax should be:

```css
@custom-variant dark (&:where(.dark, .dark *));
```

or 

```css
@custom-variant dark (&:is(.dark *));
```

